            <a href="/" class="navbar-brand px-5 text-white fs-4"><img style="width: 25px;" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/31/Apple_logo_white.svg/800px-Apple_logo_white.svg.png" alt=""></a>
